# Data Model

Create the minimum schema required.

Avoid generic structures.

Preferred approach:

```
HomepageStatistic
```

Each record should represent exactly one homepage statistic.

Recommended columns:

```text
id

page_id

order

number

title

description

is_visible

created_at

updated_at
```

No JSON blobs.

No polymorphic storage.

No generic "content" field.

Every field should have clear meaning.

